data.description: *****Sellers Willing To Assist With Closing Costs With Accepted Offer******  Welcome to your FUTURE HOME in the heart of the desirable Split Oak Estates community. This stunning property not only offers the perfect location, you also have an exclusive opportunity to take advantage of a rate buy down program in conjunction with our trusted lender partner and enjoy reduced rates, making this DREAM HOME more AFFORDABLE! You will be enamored with the endless high-end upgrades along with the combination of comfort, great location, and beautiful water views. This home located on a premium lot, features 4 bedrooms plus office, large bonus room and 3.5 bathrooms and energy saving solar panels.  Upon entering the home, you will be delighted with the spacious open floor plan with family room, dining area, and kitchen all integrated perfect for family gatherings.  The Gourmet Style Kitchen has an extended island, upgraded stainless-steel appliances, induction cooktop, built-in oven and microwave, along with soaring custom cabinets. Entertain like a pro on your expansive extended lanai showcasing a top notch outdoor kitchen with grill, 2 refrigerators, and bar with sound system. Cool off in the sparkling and refreshing salt-chlorinated Pool and Spa or take in some rays on the Sun Shelf. Pool also features  digitally controlled LED illumination and is heated. On the second level you will find a Huge Loft and a charming Owners' Suite with a spacious bathroom, dual sinks, granite countertops, walk-in super shower, and a massive walk-in closet. Secondary bedroom has a convenient en-suite bathroom, and completing the second level are two additional bedrooms and a separate full bath. Premium Home Warranty included for peace of mind. This Lot is one of the best in the community; facing north, side by side with the Club House with an amazing serene pond view with breathtaking sunsets. With almost 4,000 sqft. of heated area plus 2,200 sqft. of paved and screened yard, this home also has a spacious 3-Car garage with brick paver driveway. Enjoy the convenience of living only minutes from Orlando International Airport, 5 minutes to grocery stores, and 10 minutes from a variety of shops and restaurants, gyms, hospitals, and great public schools. It's time to live the great lifestyle that Central Florida has to offer! Seize this opportunity this to make this home of your dreams a reality. Schedule a tour today!
